CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FOne of the first lung transplant
OL,8,Fpatients to have a skin patch from
OL,9,Ftheir donor grafted onto them in a bid
OL,10,Fto spot organ rejection faster has
OL,11,Fhailed the method for helping him get
OL,12,Fswifter treatment.
OL,14,FDarren White was given steroids when
OL,15,Ftests showed his body was rejecting
OL,16,Fhis new lung three months after his
OL,17,Ftransplant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FMore than a year on, the 53-year-old
OL,8,Fis doing well and said he can be "more
OL,9,Fof a dad" to his toddler because he is
OL,10,Fable to walk and take him to the park.
OL,12,FExperts leading the Sentinel trial
OL,13,Fsaid the skin patch, which is grafted
OL,14,Fonto the forearm of patients at the
OL,15,Fsame time as their lung transplant,
OL,16,Facts as a "window".
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@IO]xD@KOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FScientists believe the skin rejects
OL,8,Fearlier than other organs and is more
OL,9,Fvisible, meaning medics can treat
OL,10,Frejection as soon as a rash appears
OL,11,Fand slash the risk of permanent damage.
OL,13,FSo far, 10 patients have received 10cm
OL,14,Fby 3cm skin patches from their organ
OL,15,Fdonor as part of the study.
OL,17,FMr White, a former bus driver from
OL,18,FStockton-on-Tees, had a lung
OL,19,Ftransplant in late 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FEarlier the same year he was diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith lung fibrosis, which causes the
OL,9,Flungs to become scarred and makes
OL,10,Fbreathing difficult.
OL,12,FHe said he did not hesitate to say yes
OL,13,Fwhen approached about the Sentinel
OL,14,Ftrial while on the waiting list.
OL,16,F"Anything that might help to avoid
OL,17,Frejection was worth a try," Mr White
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,F"Rejection is the biggest fear of any
OL,8,Ftransplant recipient, so having
OL,9,Fsomething that might be able to catch
OL,10,Fit much sooner than otherwise, was
OL,11,Freally appealing."
OL,13,FAccording to NHS Blood and Transplant
OL,14,F(NHSBT), lung rejection is hard to
OL,15,Fdetect as it can involve blood tests,
OL,16,Fbiopsies and X rays.
OL,18,FRates of rejection are highest in the
OL,19,Ffirst three to six months post-
OL,20,Fsurgery, and happen in almost a third
OL,21,Fof patients.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FThree months after having his
OL,8,Ftransplant, Mr White noticed a purple
OL,9,Frash on the skin patch and sent photos
OL,10,Fto medics.
OL,12,FA biopsy showed mild rejection and he
OL,13,Fwas treated with steroids.
OL,15,F"I definitely believe the skin patch
OL,16,Fhelped to stop the lungs from being
OL,17,Frejected," Mr White said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,F"I was feeling fine, there was no
OL,8,Freason for me to think that the lungs
OL,9,Fwere being rejected, the only sign was
OL,10,Fthe rash.
OL,12,F"I'm over a year post-transplant now
OL,13,Fand doing really well. Who knows if
OL,14,Fthat would be the case if the rash
OL,15,Fhadn't shown up and rejection wasn't
OL,16,Fspotted until further down the line."
OL,18,FMr White, who is a father to Daniel,
OL,19,Fthree, said he hopes the trial shows
OL,20,Fskin patches are a viable way of
OL,21,Fdetecting organ rejection early.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
