PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FSpeaking about life post-transplant,
OL,8,Fhe said: "The biggest difference is I
OL,9,Fcan walk, I can take Daniel to the
OL,10,Fpark to play. Before he could sit on
OL,11,Fmy knee, drive my buggy but that was
OL,12,Fit, I couldn't do much with him. I can
OL,13,Fbe more of a dad now.
OL,15,F"My favourite thing is to go to the
OL,16,Fpark, Daniel always asks to go on the
OL,17,Fswing and we have one in our garden. I
OL,18,Fcan push him now. It's the simple
OL,19,Fthings that are the best, we both love
OL,20,Fit."
OL,26,@pD@JOUwD@AOU|D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
