CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FThe Sentinel trial is set to run until
OL,8,F2027 and will recruit 152 patients at
OL,9,Ffive centres; Freeman Hospital,
OL,10,FHarefield Hospital, Queen Elizabeth
OL,11,FHospital, Royal Papworth and
OL,12,FWythenshawe Hospital.
OL,14,FThe skin grafts are carried out by
OL,15,Fplastic surgeons at the University of
OL,16,FOxford.
OL,18,FThe method has been used previously in
OL,19,Fpatients receiving intestinal
OL,20,Ftransplants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FThe families of donors must consent
OL,8,Ffor the skin transplant to take place
OL,9,Fvia NHSBT specialist nurses.
OL,11,FHenk Giele, chief investigator of
OL,12,FSentinel and an Oxford plastic surgeon
OL,13,Fsaid: "It seems logical that having a
OL,14,Fwindow to your transplant can provide
OL,15,Fan early warning system of rejection
OL,16,For reassure you that you don't have
OL,17,Frejection but we have to prove it
OL,18,Fworks.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,F"We are so grateful to the patients,
OL,8,Fthe donors and their families, the
OL,9,Ftransplant teams, and the NHSBT staff
OL,10,Fwho make this important trial happen.
OL,11,FWe hope it will change what we know
OL,12,Fabout transplant and makes patients
OL,13,Flives better and longer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
