FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775624629
OL,3,CSkin patch from organ donor helped
OL,4,Cpatient spot his new lung was being
OL,5,Crejected
OL,7,FAndrew Fisher, a professor of
OL,8,Frespiratory transplant medicine at
OL,9,FNewcastle University, honorary
OL,10,Fconsultant respiratory physician at
OL,11,FNewcastle Hospitals and the lead for
OL,12,FSentinel in Newcastle, added: "If
OL,13,Fsuccessful, this approach has the
OL,14,Fpotential to revolutionise the way
OL,15,Flung transplants are performed in the
OL,16,Ffuture and reduce the problems with
OL,17,Fdetecting and treating rejection
OL,18,Fearly, which is vital."
OL,26,@tD@_OUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
